European Recipes become difficult when you are unable to figure out the measurements
========================================================

**Metric System**
- Dry: Grams
- Liquid: Milletres

**US**
- Cups dry
- Cups liquid

Conversions to cups can make cooking European Delicates a reality
========================================================
**Here are the calculations:**

$$
LiquidCups = \frac{Millitres}{236.588}
$$
 
$$
Cups = \frac{Grams}{236.588}
$$

$$
Ounces = \frac{Grams}{28.35}
$$

